{"tid":212684,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[莫縮叔台] INSIDE (PC)","createTime":"2017-04-22T15:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T15:46:04.000Z","uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"467a7858e3be959f945102f16a88b83e847cd3a3","tid":212684,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"[莫縮叔台] INSIDE (PC)<br />\n<br />\n莫縮叔遊戲台<br />\n每個星期五、六、日晚上，<br />\n跟大家一邊傾計，一邊打機<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmokuncle%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7ae2e82f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/86/INSIDE_Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F86%2FINSIDE_Cover.jpg&h=d715e2e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Inside》是一款由獨立遊戲工作室Playdead所開發及發行的平台解謎及冒險遊戲。遊戲無論在主題及視覺上均類似同一公司的另一款作品《地獄邊境》，玩家需扮演一名小男孩，在黑白色的遊戲環境中解決不同的難題，並同時避免在3D滾動時死亡。 <br />\n資料來源：維基百科<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n莫縮叔Facebook Page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMokUncle&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=371f96dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle</a>"}]}